%% Data Flow Diagram - llm-d-inference-scheduler
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Envoy as Envoy Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP (Endpoint Picker)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Sidecar as P/D Routing Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Prefill as Prefill Pod (vLLM)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Decoder as Local vLLM Decoder<br/>8001/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant VLLMEvt as vLLM Instances<br/>5557/TCP ZeroMQ

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Standard Inference (No P/D)
    Client->>Envoy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    Envoy->>EPP: ext-proc request<br/>gRPC/9002 (plaintext)
    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool/Pods<br/>HTTPS/443 (ServiceAccount)
    EPP-->>Envoy: Selected pod endpoint<br/>gRPC/9002
    Envoy->>Decoder: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Disaggregated P/D (NIXL v2)
    Client->>Envoy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    Envoy->>EPP: ext-proc request<br/>gRPC/9002 (plaintext)
    Note over EPP: pd-profile selects<br/>prefill + decode pods
    EPP-->>Envoy: Decode pod + prefill headers<br/>gRPC/9002
    Envoy->>Sidecar: Forward to decode pod<br/>HTTP(S)/8000
    Sidecar->>Prefill: Prefill request<br/>HTTP(S) + kv_transfer_params
    Prefill-->>Sidecar: Prefill response<br/>with KV transfer metadata
    Sidecar->>Decoder: Decode request<br/>HTTP(S)/8001
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Streaming tokens
    Sidecar-->>Envoy: Response stream<br/>HTTP(S)/8000
    Envoy-->>Client: Inference response

    Note over VLLMEvt,EPP: Flow 3: KV Cache Event Streaming
    VLLMEvt->>EPP: KV cache events<br/>ZeroMQ/5557 (plaintext)
    Note over EPP: Updates internal<br/>KV cache index for<br/>precise prefix scoring
